These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, chef, teacher, designer
1. the designer is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
2. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the designer##5
3. the chef is not to the left of the teacher##8
4. the chef is on the left of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Job   | teacher | chef | designer | fisherman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, iced-tea, sprite
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
2. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking iced-tea##2
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |  2   |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea | almond-milk | sprite |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-3::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, carrot, artichoke, radish
1. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person eating carrot##5
2. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating radish##1
3. the person eating carrot is not to the left of the person eating radish##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |   2   |   3    |   4    |
| Food   | apple | radish | carrot | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, reading, board-games, photography
1. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is reading##7
2. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2      |       3       |   4    |
| Hobby   | reading | photography | board-games | card-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-5::.
