2. the person eating grapes is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating grapes is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
4. the person eating grapes is the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |     3     |   4   |
| Food   | cauliflower | avocado | grapes | orange |

