2. the fan of d&b is between the fan of ambient and the fan of reggae##2
3. the fan of reggae is not to the right of the fan of gospel##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2  |   3    |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | d&b | reggae | gospel |

